id: pm-nilh
title: "GH-437: make lean mutation output the CLI default (parity with MCP compact envelope)"
description: "Dogfood GH-437: CLI mutations echo the full item (12.7x vs --id-only) while MCP is compact by default; align CLI default with MCP. Duplicate check: compact mutation output PR (2026-05-26) shipped suppressor flags only; no open item flips the default."
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,"area:cli",gh-issue,token-efficiency
